{"payload": {"model": "glm-4-flash-250414", "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "你是少样本时序分类专家。给你 K=6 个有标签的训练样本和 1 个 query 序列，请输出 query 的 class。\n\n候选 class: [1, 2]\n\n【训练样本】\n  [0] label=1: mean=0.000, std=0.999, first=['1.25', '1.17', '1.07', '0.96', '0.90', '0.79'], last=['0.87', '0.96', '1.06', '1.13', '1.22', '1.29']\n  [1] label=1: mean=-0.000, std=0.999, first=['2.01', '1.94', '1.93', '1.86', '1.78', '1.71'], last=['1.43', '1.51', '1.58', '1.72', '1.86', '1.94']\n  [2] label=1: mean=-0.000, std=0.999, first=['1.79', '1.80', '1.78', '1.73', '1.63', '1.53'], last=['1.20', '1.30', '1.40', '1.48', '1.61', '1.71']\n  [3] label=2: mean=-0.000, std=0.999, first=['2.51', '2.48', '2.45', '2.43', '2.42', '2.37'], last=['2.23', '2.30', '2.37', '2.39', '2.46', '2.48']\n  [4] label=2: mean=0.000, std=0.999, first=['1.50', '1.49', '1.40', '1.28', '1.12', '0.98'], last=['0.68', '0.84', '0.98', '1.12', '1.25', '1.43']\n  [5] label=2: mean=0.000, std=0.999, first=['1.40', '1.37', '1.25', '1.09', '0.93', '0.81'], last=['0.63', '0.80', '0.92', '1.04', '1.20', '1.32']\n\n【Query 序列】\nmean=0.000, std=0.999, first=['2.13', '2.17', '2.16', '2.14', '2.09', '1.98'], last=['1.70', '1.78', '1.87', '1.93', '2.02', '2.08']\n\n输出 JSON（仅 JSON）：\n{\n  \"class\": <one of [1, 2]>,\n  \"confidence\": <0-1 float>,\n  \"reason\": \"<1 句话>\"\n}\n"}], "temperature": 0.1, "max_tokens": 1024}, "content": "```json\n{\n  \"class\": 2,\n  \"confidence\": 0.95,\n  \"reason\": \"The query sequence's mean and standard deviation are similar to those of the label 2 samples, and its first and last values are closer to the corresponding values of label 2 samples than to label 1 samples.\"\n}\n```"}